headline: Will 3M's (MMM) Indonesia Manufacturing Deal Redefine Its Energy Sector Growth Story?
summary: PT Pipa Mas Putih recently announced a partnership with 3M to manufacture 3M™ Ceramic Sand Screens in Indonesia, combining 3M's global technology with local production to serve high-pressure energy applications. This collaboration is expected to boost delivery speed, operational efficiency, and reliability for regional energy operators, supporting Indonesia's energy independence and resilience.
